Copyright (c) 2025-2026 KOOWEXA. All rights reserved.

**It is strictly forbidden** to use, copy, modify, adapt, translate, reverse engineer, distribute, republish, or employ **under any concept of utility or use** –whether commercial, educational, personal, or otherwise– the design, coding, structure, images, texts, logo, or any other element contained in this platform (repository and official website), **without the express written consent of KOOWEXA**.

This prohibition includes, but is not limited to:

- Using the source code or design to create another website, application, or similar service.
- Extracting code or design fragments to integrate into your own or third-party projects.
- Taking the visual or functional structure as inspiration to recreate an equivalent system.
- Using the system for demonstration, hands-on learning, or training without authorization.

### Sole permitted use

Only **viewing the source code in this repository for transparency auditing** is allowed, provided that no action of copying, automated downloading, local execution, or any other form of active use is performed. Mere browser viewing of the GitHub repository does not constitute a usage permit.

### Infringements

Any violation of these terms will be legally pursued under applicable Cuban and international laws, including intellectual property, data protection, and unfair competition regulations.

